WEBVTT


00:00:00.277 --> 00:00:01.200
Good news!

00:00:01.361 --> 00:00:03.810
for those who have 1 part-time contract

00:00:03.811 --> 00:00:06.301
are going to contribute as if they were working full time,

00:00:06.302 --> 00:00:06.927
Dusiles? 

00:00:06.927 --> 00:00:07.901
Indeed Sandra,

00:00:07.902 --> 00:00:08.490
from now on, 

00:00:08.490 --> 00:00:09.214
those who work, 

00:00:09.214 --> 00:00:09.712
for example

00:00:09.997 --> 00:00:10.301
e.g. 

00:00:10.301 --> 00:00:11.641
4 hours per day of 2nd

00:00:12.120 --> 00:00:13.492
which will be 1/2 day,

00:00:13.608 --> 00:00:16.156
are going to pay social security contributions as if they were working.

00:00:16.248 --> 00:00:18.092
8 hours for the full day.

00:00:18.208 --> 00:00:19.736
You will benefit from this change

00:00:19.768 --> 00:00:22.792
3 million people with part-time contracts,

00:00:22.808 --> 00:00:24.094
the majority, 

00:00:24.094 --> 00:00:25.105
about 70%, 

00:00:25.105 --> 00:00:25.932
are women
